Lothar, the Master of the Bones, is a frighteningly high-level priest living beneath the Lower Ward of Sigil. He collects skulls of all kinds and reads their memories. He is served by wererats, which Tattershade loans him.
Lothar appeared as a character in Plugin &lt;em&gt;&lt;/em&gt; Not Found. 

